title: May Debuts: Not Reading would be "a complete disaster"
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being May 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.



This instalment contains:



   Dream Police #1 - Image Comics  - Alternate Reality / Mystery / Noir

   Henchmen     #1 - (Independent) - Crime / Humour / Superhero

   MPH          #1 - Image Comics  - Action / Crime / Superhero

   The Woods    #1 - Boom Studios  - Adventure / Disaster / Sci-Fi



As a bonus, you get the clearly closely related "Dream Police" singleton published in 2005 by Marvel ( <a href=" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dream_Police_(comics)" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dream_Police_(comics)</a>  ), despite the peculiar lack of any reference to it in the author's notes for the 2014 Image debut.
